Conrad Nagel https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Conrad_Nagel 0 Conrad Nagel ((1897-03-16)March 16, 1897 – (1970-02-24)February 24, 1970) was an American screen actor and matinee idol of the silent film era and beyond. He was also a well-known sound film and television and radio performer.
